column5: Sweet Brownie Miller, You hava had a good couple of months   Clarence
Nice Brown WTG!!
Wow another beauty !! Congrats
HOLLY MOLLY thats a cow.
thanks guys, i think it'll be a while before i can top that one haha
Keep at'er Miller.  It can be done.  That's the biggest I've seen in a few months though!  Great stuff.
hit the softwater before work today and it paid off 19lbs 1oz    self timer shot
Giant fish, did you eat it?
released to make many more with that gene pool   hahah. i'm not a fan of eating trout i stick to crappie, walleye and perch
Wow  Thats a Sweet Browny! Congrats on one heck of a catch. (Jealous am I LOL!)
Awesome fish.  If I didn't have three days off for ice fishing next week, I would have been hitting the softwater for steelies.  What a beautiful day!!
Beauty.
Nice fish!  Congrats on the PB!
I believe you that it's 19.  It's a great catch Miller, it'll be tough to break that PB. He must have smashed that Mepps.
Nice brute.! Makes for a good story to tell at work.
TANK  Great catch...
That's a great looking fish    Congrats miller
Wow!!   Great fish.  Congrats, you don't see tanks like that very often.
Could it get any fatter.  Nice catch.
wow.  what a slob!
CHA CHA CHA!!! Congrats.  What a piggy.
saaaaaaaaaaaaweet!! nice shootin
Nice catch buddy. We will have to get out when I am good.
Awsome fish bro!
That's a beast.  Second 18lb + brown I saw reported from yesterday. Crazy
Don't see that many browns quite that large, very impressive!
Very nice fish, solo is right, that is a rare beaut.
solo i'll send you a pic of one my friend got last week. makes my brown look small.
Wow! What a hog! Keep it up man!   TDunn
Just getting rewarded for your dedication there Miller.  Way to go!
This Brown is huge!  Great job on your PB!
